    "html_format": "<div class=\"document-view-wrapper\">\n<style>\n.html-preview * {font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview a.NoteRef {text-decoration: none;}\n.html-preview table td {vertical-align: top;}\n.html-preview table {width: 100%;}\n.html-preview p {white-space: pre-wrap;}\n.html-preview .leading {width: 4px; display: inline-block;}\n.html-preview hr {height: 1px; padding: 0; margin: 1em 0; border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #CCC;}\n.html-preview .Normal {className: Normal; margin-bottom: 10pt;}\n.html-preview .a3 {font-family: 'AntiquaUz'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;}\n.html-preview .Text {font-family: 'AntiquaUz'; font-size: 12pt;}\n</style>\n<div class=\"html-preview\">\n<style>.html-preview{width: 762px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-top: 76px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-bottom: 32px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-left: 81px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-right: 57px}</style><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">Васиятномани бекор қилиш ҳақидаги ариза</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Ўзбекистон Республикаси,</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-2\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#2}Ариза киритилаётган нотариал идора манзили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">,</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-5 structure-5\" style=\"className:5 5; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; display: none;\">{#5}Хусусий амалиёт билан шуғулланувчи нотариус Ф.И.О.</span><span class=\"structures structure-5\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; display: none;\">{#5}га</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#6}__-сон давлат нотариал идорасига</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-7\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#7}Аризачининг яшаш манзили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">,</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#11}Аризачи рўйхатдан ўтган уй рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">-уйда яшовчи</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-12\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#12}Аризачининг Ф.И.О. </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">дан</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic;\">(паспорт </span><span class=\"structures structure-13\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic;\">{#13}Аризачининг паспорт серияси ва рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic;\">,<span class=\"leading\"></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-14\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic;\">{#14}Аризачига паспорт берган ИИБ (ҳудуд) номи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic;\"> </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic;\"> томонидан </span><span class=\"structures structure-15\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic;\">{#15}Аризачига паспорт берилган сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic;\"> йилда берилган)</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 266.46666666667px;\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 313.73333333333px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; color: #auto; font-weight: bold;\">А<span class=\"leading\"></span>Р И З А</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Ўзбекистон Республикаси, </span><span class=\"structures structure-17\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#17}Ариза ёзилган ҳудуд </span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span class=\"structures structure-19\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#19}Аризанинг ёзилган санаси</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> куни</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 26.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Мен – </span><span class=\"structures structure-12\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#12}Аризачининг Ф.И.О.</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; color: #ff0000;\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">ушбу аризам билан </span><span class=\"structures structure-20\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#20}Васиятномани расмийлаштирган нотариус идораси манзили </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-22\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; display: none;\">{#22}Хусусий амалиёт билан шуғулланувчи <span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-22 structure-26\" style=\"className:22 26; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; display: none;\">{#22}Нотариуснинг Ф.И.О.</span><span class=\"structures structure-23\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#23}-сон давлат нотариал идораси</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> нотариуси </span><span class=\"structures structure-26\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#26}Нотариуснинг Ф.И.О.</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">томонидан </span><span class=\"structures structure-24\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#24}Васиятнома берилган сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">да </span><span class=\"structures structure-25\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#25}Васиятнома қайд қилинган рақам </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> реестр рақами билан қайд қилинган васиятномамни бекор қиламан.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Аризанинг матнини тўлиқ ўқиб чиқдим, унинг мазмуни ва моҳияти, ҳуқуқий оқибатлари менга нотариус томонидан тушунтирилди ва тушунарли, аризанинг мазмуни менинг асл хоҳиш-истакларимга мос келади.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-style: italic;\">Нотариуснинг тасдиқлов ёзуви</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 28.4px;\"></p>\n</div></div>",
